      <bioghist>
         <head>Biographical/Historical Information</head>
         <p>Pastors: John Jasper 1867-1901 Randolph Payton 1902-1922 A.
         W. Brown 1924-1967 Barry Hopkins 1968- Isadore Mims 1972-1991
         John Johnson 1993-</p>
      </bioghist>
      <scopecontent>
         <head>Scope and Content Information</head>
         <p>The collection consists of an assortment of historical
         documents, programs, photographs, brochures and clippings
         concerning the church, its pastors and Jackson Ward.</p>
      </scopecontent>
